# 1. Ignore everything
*

# 2. Allow the essentials
!.gitignore
!README.md
!requirements.txt

# 3. Allow all Jupyter Notebooks
!*.ipynb

# 4. Specifically ignore those annoying Windows Zone Identifier files
*:Zone.Identifier

# 5. Ensure the big folders stay ignored even if you try to add them
MASRI/
Runs/
Language_Models/
SampleAudios/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
